Title: Daily: Line em up
Descriptions: Survivors! The ancient titans loom large, a constant shadow over our fragile existence. We issue a bold decree: vanquish not a mere 25, not even 100, but a mind-boggling 5 of these colossal creatures that roam our lands! The drumbeat of danger grows ever louder, and in this trial by fire, your courage becomes our shield. Let this be the week where our resilience knows no bounds! Unite against these primordial giants, fortify our camp's defenses, and claim the rewards that await the brave! Arvandus Metalsmith calls upon you to defy the odds. Will you heed the call and emerge victorious?
